# Approval Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get all approvals (protected, director)
GET http://localhost:3001/approvals?status=PENDING&type=all
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get approval by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/approvals/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update approval status (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/approvals/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "APPROVED",
  "note": "Looks good"
}
